        ║  LEADER CONSTELLATION — 56 Nodes, 5 Branches            ║
        ║  Layout: Crown — Diplomacy(NW) / Commerce(NE) /         ║
        ║          Governance(SW) / Command(SE) + Rally(N)         ║
        ║                                                          ║
        ║  Branches:                                               ║
        ║   • DIPLOMACY   (NW) — Negotiation, SocialImpact        ║
