        ║   • GOVERNANCE  (SW) — ArrestSuccess, MentalBreakThresh  ║
        ║   • COMMAND     (SE) — Taming, TrainAnimal               ║
        ║   • RALLY       (N)  — gimmick nodes + SocialImpact core ║
        ║   + 5 cross-connectors between adjacent branches         ║
        ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
    -->
    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Leader</defName>
        <label>Leader</label>
        <treeClass>Leader</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Natural commanders who amplify the colony's potential through sheer force of personality. Five constellations radiate from the leader's core — each representing a different dimension of authority. The larger the colony they command, the more effective their Rallying Presence becomes.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>RallyingPresence</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Rallying Presence</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>The Leader's social effectiveness scales with colony size. More free colonists means stronger social impact, negotiation, and trade prices. Rallying Presence scales along the Rally Path. Tier 1 (Rallying Cry): +2% per colonist, max 8 counted (max +16%). Tier 2 (Battle Standard): +2.5% per colonist, max 12 counted (max +30%). Tier 3 (Champion's Aura): +3% per colonist, max 16 counted (max +48%). Tier 4 (Supreme Commander): +3.5% per colonist, max 20 counted (max +70%). The bigger the colony, the more powerful the Leader becomes.</classGimmickDescription>

