                <nodeId>LD_GV_LawAndOrder</nodeId>
                <label>Law and Order</label>
                <description>You embody the rule of law. Prisoners cannot resist your authority, colonists cannot defy it, and even raiders hesitate when they see you standing firm. Your colony runs with the precision of a well-oiled machine because everyone knows their role — and everyone knows who's in charge.\n\nTRADEOFF: Your rigid discipline leaves little room for physical agility.</description>
